<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Mang Crinkle Order is on its Way!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    /* Shipping Details */
    .shipping-details {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .shipping-details-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .shipping-detail-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
    }
    
    .shipping-detail-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .shipping-detail-label {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .shipping-detail-value {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .tracking-highlight {
      background-color: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    /* Line Items Table - matching admin-table styling */
    .line-items-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .line-items-table thead {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .line-items-table th {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
    
    .line-items-table th.text-center {
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .line-items-table th.text-right {
      text-align: right;
    }
    
    .line-items-table td {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: white;
    }
    
    .line-items-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    .item-name {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #7e2a0c;
    }
    
    .item-description {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    
    .item-details {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    
    .item-details-header {
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    
    .item-details-list {
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    
    .item-price {
      text-align: center;
      color: #ea580c;
    }
    
    .item-price-right {
      text-align: right;
      color: #ea580c;
    }
    
    .table-footer {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .table-footer td {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    
    /* Admin Button - matching admin-btn-primary with correct hover */
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f54900;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #ca3500;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">Mang Crinkle</div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">Your Order is on its Way!</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">Order #<%= @order.id %> has shipped</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello <%= @order.user&.display_name || @order.customer_name %>,</p>
          
          <p>Great news! Your Mang Crinkle order has been packed with love and is now on its way to you!</p>
          
          <div class="shipping-details">
            <div class="shipping-details-title">Shipping Information</div>
            
            <div class="shipping-detail-row">
              <span class="shipping-detail-label">Order Number:</span>
              <span class="shipping-detail-value">#<%= @order.id %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="shipping-detail-row">
              <span class="shipping-detail-label">Tracking Number:</span>
              <span class="shipping-detail-value">
                <span class="tracking-highlight"><%= @order.tracking_number %></span>
              </span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="shipping-detail-row">
              <span class="shipping-detail-label">Carrier:</span>
              <span class="shipping-detail-value"><%= @order.carrier || @order.shipping_company %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="shipping-detail-row">
              <span class="shipping-detail-label">Estimated Delivery:</span>
              <span class="shipping-detail-value"><%= @order.estimated_delivery.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <% if @order.line_items.any? %>
            <div class="content-section">
              <h3 style="color: #7e2a0c; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Items Shipped</h3>
              
              <table class="line-items-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Item</th>
                    <th class="text-center">Qty</th>
                    <th class="text-center">Price</th>
                    <th class="text-right">Total</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <% @order.line_items.each do |item| %>
                    <tr>
                      <td>
                        <div class="item-name"><%= item.purchasable.name %></div>
                        <% if item.description.present? %>
                          <div class="item-description"><%= item.description %></div>
                        <% end %>
                        <% if item.purchasable.is_a?(CrinklePackage) && item.selected_products.any? %>
                          <div class="item-details">
                            <div class="item-details-header">Selected items:</div>
                            <% item.selected_products.each do |selected| %>
                              <div class="item-details-list">â€¢ <%= selected[:quantity] %>x <%= selected[:product].name %></div>
                            <% end %>
                          </div>
                        <% end %>
                      </td>
                      <td class="item-price"><%= item.quantity %></td>
                      <td class="item-price">$<%= sprintf('%.2f', item.price) %></td>
                      <td class="item-price-right">$<%= sprintf('%.2f', item.quantity * item.price) %></td>
                    </tr>
                  <% end %>
                </tbody>
                <tfoot class="table-footer">
                  <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" style="text-align: right;">Total:</td>
                    <td style="text-align: right;">$<%= sprintf('%.2f', @order.total_price) %></td>
                  </tr>
                </tfoot>
              </table>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          
          <% if @order.address.present? %>
            <div class="content-section">
              <h3 style="color: #7e2a0c; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Delivery Address</h3>
              <div style="background-color: #fff7ed; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; margin: 0;">
                <%= simple_format(@order.address) %>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <h3 style="color: #7e2a0c; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">What's Next?</h3>
            <p>Use your tracking number to monitor your package's progress. You'll receive updates as your order makes its way to you!</p>
            <p>Once your delicious treats arrive, store them in a cool, dry place and enjoy within 7 days for the best taste and freshness.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.order_url(@order, host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">Track Your Order</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>Shipped on: <%= Date.current.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
          <p>Questions about your order? Reply to this email or contact us at <%= company_email %></p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>With love and fresh-baked goodness,<br>
            <span class="signature-name">The Mang Crinkle Team</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 